<topic id="documentumcms-actions-at-connection-level">
  <title><?oxy_comment_start author="steven_higgs" timestamp="20160307T162308+0200" comment="Merged or no longer needed. Moved to not_used folder.  "?>Actions
    Available on Connection<?oxy_comment_end?></title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords><indexterm>Documentum (CMS)
            Support<indexterm>actions<indexterm>connection</indexterm></indexterm></indexterm></keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>The contextual menu of a <ph
        keyref="documentumCMS"/> connection
      in the <uicontrol>Data Source Explorer</uicontrol> view offers the following actions:</p>
    <dl>
      <dlentry>
        <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/OptionsShortcut16.gif" id="image_efp_ckt_tr"/>Configure
            Database Sources</uicontrol></dt>
        <dd>Opens the <i>Data Sources </i>
          <xref href="preferences-database.dita">preferences page</xref> where you can configure
          both data sources and connections.</dd>
      </dlentry>
      <dlentry>
        <dt><uicontrol>New Cabinet</uicontrol></dt>
        <dd>Creates a new cabinet in the repository. The cabinet properties are: <ul>
            <li><uicontrol>Type</uicontrol> - The type of the new cabinet (default is
                <uicontrol>dm_cabinet</uicontrol>).</li>
            <li><uicontrol>Name</uicontrol> - The name of the new cabinet.</li>
            <li><uicontrol>Title</uicontrol> - The title property of the cabinet.</li>
            <li><uicontrol>Subject</uicontrol> - The subject property of the cabinet.</li>
          </ul></dd>
      </dlentry>
      <dlentry>
        <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Refresh16.png" id="image_a5p_jfw_sr"
          />Refresh</uicontrol></dt>
        <dd>Refreshes the connection.</dd>
      </dlentry>
    </dl>
  </body>
